dcterms:description: A dataset containing user click logs used for training the Multi-modal Item Embedding Model (MIEM). Each log entry is represented as a triplet ⟨query image, clicked item title, clicked item image list⟩.
dcterms:title: User Click Logs Dataset

dcterms:description: A dataset based on real-world user queries collected from the Indonesia market, containing user query images and 3 million Shopee products.
dcterms:title: User Query Dataset

dcterms:description: A dataset containing click logs used for training the MIEM model, focusing on user interactions with search results.
dcterms:title: Click Logs Dataset

dcterms:description: A dataset used for the same item merging strategy, annotated by external annotators to determine whether products are the same.
dcterms:title: External Annotators' Dataset

dcterms:description: A triplet dataset consisting of query images, clicked item titles, and lists of clicked item images, used for training the MIEM model.
dcterms:title: Triplet Dataset
